<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ka">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ხის სახლები — ბავშვის ოცნება</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Nunito:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --pink:      #F2A7C3;
    --pink-deep: #E07AA0;
    --purple:    #9B72CF;
    --purple-deep:#7A4FB5;
    --lavender:  #D4B8F0;
    --cream:     #FFF5F9;
    --white:     #FFFFFF;
    --dark:      #2D1B3D;
    --text:      #5A4060;
    --wood:      #C49A5A;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--dark); overflow-x: hidden; }

  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 56px;
    background: rgba(255,245,249,0.94); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.15);
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.45rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--purple-deep); }
  .logo span { color: var(--pink-deep); }
  nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 32px; }
  nav ul a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.88rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
  nav ul a:hover { color: var(--purple-deep); }

  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F8D7E8 0%, #E8C8F8 50%, #D4B8F0 100%);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center; padding: 120px 56px 80px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden; gap: 48px;
  }
  .hearts { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .heart { position: absolute; animation: float linear infinite; opacity: 0.2; }
  @keyframes float {
    0%   { transform: translateY(100vh); opacity: 0; }
    10%  { opacity: 0.2; }
    90%  { opacity: 0.2; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-10vh); opacity: 0; }
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); border: 1.5px solid var(--pink);
    color: var(--purple-deep); padding: 7px 20px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 26px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4.5vw, 4.4rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 20px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.12s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--purple-deep); font-style: normal; }
  .hero p { color: var(--text); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 40px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.24s ease both; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.36s ease both; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-deep), var(--pink-deep));
    color: white; padding: 15px 36px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(122,79,181,0.35); transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(122,79,181,0.45); }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 2px solid var(--purple-deep); color: var(--purple-deep);
    padding: 13px 32px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(155,114,207,0.1); }

  .hero-img { position: relative; z-index: 2; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both; }
  .hero-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 28px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(122,79,181,0.25); }

  .stats {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-deep), var(--pink-deep));
    padding: 44px 56px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 72px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat-item { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 900; color: white; display: block; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 4px; display: block; }

  .section-header { text-align: center; padding: 80px 56px 52px; }
  .section-tag { display: inline-block; color: var(--purple-deep); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .section-header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.2; }
  .section-header p { margin-top: 14px; color: var(--text); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.7; }

  .catalog-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 28px; padding: 0 56px 80px; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card {
    background: white; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(122,79,181,0.09);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.12);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .card:hover { transform: translateY(-7px); box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(122,79,181,0.18); }

  .card-img { height: 250px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FCE4F0, #EDD4FC); }
  .card-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s; }
  .card:hover .card-img img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .card-img svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }

  .card-badge { position: absolute; top: 14px; left: 14px; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; }
  .badge-new { background: var(--purple-deep); color: white; }
  .badge-pop { background: var(--pink-deep); color: white; }
  .badge-best { background: var(--wood); color: white; }

  .card-body { padding: 26px; }
  .card-body h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .card-body p { color: var(--text); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .card-specs { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .spec { background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.2); border-radius: 50px; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.77rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--purple-deep); }
  .card-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-top: 18px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.1); }
  .price { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--purple-deep); }
  .price span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #aaa; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; }
  .btn-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-deep), var(--pink-deep)); color: white; padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; }
  .btn-card:hover { opacity: 0.88; transform: scale(1.03); }

  #sizes { background: white; }
  .sizes-wrap { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 56px 80px; }
  .sizes-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(122,79,181,0.1); }
  .sizes-table th { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-deep), var(--pink-deep)); color: white; padding: 16px 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; }
  .sizes-table td { padding: 14px 20px; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.92rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.08); }
  .sizes-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .sizes-table tr:hover td { background: var(--cream); }
  .sizes-table td:first-child { font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark); }
  .hl { color: var(--purple-deep); font-weight: 800; }

  #about { background: var(--cream); }
  .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; padding: 0 56px 80px; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .feature-card { background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 34px 26px; text-align: center; border: 1.5px solid rgba(155,114,207,0.12); box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(122,79,181,0.06); transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
  .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(122,79,181,0.14); }
  .feature-icon { font-size: 2.8rem; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .feature-card h4 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .feature-card p { color: var(--text); font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.65; }

  #contact { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-deep) 0%, var(--pink-deep) 100%); padding: 80px 56px; }
  .contact-wrap { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; }
  .contact-info h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900; color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .contact-info p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .contact-detail { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: white; margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .contact-form { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .form-group label { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select { width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 15px; color: white; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; font-size: 0.92rem; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .form-group input::placeholder, .form-group textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
  .form-group select option { background: var(--purple-deep); }
  .form-group textarea { height: 100px; resize: vertical; }
  .btn-submit { width: 100%; background: white; color: var(--purple-deep); padding: 14px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.98rem; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; }
  .btn-submit:hover { opacity: 0.92; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  footer { background: var(--dark); padding: 26px 56px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; }
  footer .logo { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  footer p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 0.83rem; }

  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(26px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 14px 22px; }
    nav ul { display: none; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 100px 22px 60px; gap: 32px; }
    .stats { padding: 36px 22px; gap: 36px; }
    .section-header { padding: 60px 22px 40px; }
    .catalog-grid { padding: 0 22px 60px; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .features-grid { padding: 0 22px 60px; }
    .sizes-wrap { padding: 0 22px 60px; }
    .contact-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    #contact { padding: 60px 22px; }
    footer { padding: 22px; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hearts" id="hearts"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">🏡 ხის<span>სახლი</span></div>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#catalog">კატალოგი</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sizes">ზომები</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">ჩვენს შესახებ</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">შეკვეთა</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">💜 ხელნაკეთი · ეკო-მასალა · ქართული წარმოება</div>
    <h1>ბავშვის <em>ოცნება</em><br>ხეში იბადება</h1>
    <p>ვქმნით ვარდისფერ-იასამნისფერ ხის სახლებს, სადაც ყოველი ბავშვი თავს განსაკუთრებულად გრძნობს. 2–3 მ² — სრულყოფილი ზომა ნებისმიერი ეზოსთვის.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#catalog" class="btn-primary">კატალოგის ნახვა →</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-outline">შეკვეთა</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-img">
    <img src="house1.jfif" alt="ვარდისფერი ხის სახლი ბავშვისთვის">
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">120+</span><span class="stat-label">ბედნიერი ოჯახი</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">8+</span><span class="stat-label">წლიანი გამოცდილება</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">100%</span><span class="stat-label">ბუნებრივი მასალა</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">1 წელი</span><span class="stat-label">გარანტია</span></div>
</div>

<section id="catalog">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-tag">🏡 ჩვენი კოლექცია</span>
    <h2>ხის სახლების კატალოგი</h2>
    <p>ფერი, დეკორი და ზომა — შენი ბავშვის ოცნების მიხედვით.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="catalog-grid">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <img src="house1.jfif" alt="ვარდის ბუდე">
        <span class="card-badge badge-new">ახალი</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3>💜 "ვარდის ბუდე" — მინი</h3>
        <p>2 მ² კომპაქტური სახლი გულის დეკორით, ვერანდით და ლამაზი სახურავით. იდეალური პატარა ეზოსთვის.</p>
        <div class="card-specs">
          <span class="spec">📐 2 მ²</span>
          <span class="spec">190×140 სმ</span>
          <span class="spec">↕ 220 სმ</span>
          <span class="spec">👶 3–8 წ.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <div class="price">₾ 2,800 <span>/ განვ.</span></div>
          <button class="btn-card" onclick="scrollContact()">შეკვეთა 💜</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 330 250" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="330" height="250" fill="#F0D4F8"/>
          <rect x="75" y="110" width="180" height="125" fill="#F2C0D8" rx="4"/>
          <polygon points="165,35 50,120 280,120" fill="#9B72CF"/>
          <polygon points="165,35 85,112 245,112" fill="#B090E8"/>
          <rect x="138" y="155" width="54" height="80" fill="#B060A0" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M163 188 a7 7 0 0 1 14 0 a7 7 0 0 1 -14 0" fill="#9B72CF"/>
          <rect x="88" y="128" width="46" height="46" fill="#E8C8F8" rx="4"/>
          <rect x="196" y="128" width="46" height="46" fill="#E8C8F8" rx="4"/>
          <text x="111" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-size="20" fill="#9B72CF">♥</text>
          <text x="219" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-size="20" fill="#9B72CF">★</text>
          <rect x="55" y="233" width="220" height="10" fill="#C49A5A" rx="3"/>
          <rect x="40" y="168" width="14" height="72" fill="#D4AA6A"/>
          <rect x="276" y="168" width="14" height="72" fill="#D4AA6A"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="card-badge badge-pop">პოპულარული</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3>🌸 "ვარდის სასახლე" — სტანდარტი</h3>
        <p>3 მ² სახლი ვრცელი ვერანდით, ორი ფანჯრით და გულისა და ვარსკვლავის დეკორით.</p>
        <div class="card-specs">
          <span class="spec">📐 3 მ²</span>
          <span class="spec">200×150 სმ</span>
          <span class="spec">↕ 230 სმ</span>
          <span class="spec">👶 4–12 წ.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <div class="price">₾ 3,900 <span>/ განვ.</span></div>
          <button class="btn-card" onclick="scrollContact()">შეკვეთა 💜</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 330 250" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="330" height="250" fill="#FCE8F4"/>
          <rect x="55" y="105" width="220" height="130" fill="#F4B8D4" rx="4"/>
          <polygon points="165,25 30,115 300,115" fill="#E07AA0"/>
          <polygon points="165,25 55,107 275,107" fill="#F090B8"/>
          <rect x="132" y="148" width="66" height="87" fill="#C04878" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M160 180 a9 9 0 0 1 18 0 a9 9 0 0 1 -18 0" fill="#E07AA0"/>
          <rect x="68" y="122" width="50" height="50" fill="#FCD8EC" rx="5"/>
          <rect x="212" y="122" width="50" height="50" fill="#FCD8EC" rx="5"/>
          <text x="93" y="152" text-anchor="middle" font-size="22" fill="#E07AA0">♥</text>
          <text x="237" y="152" text-anchor="middle" font-size="22" fill="#E07AA0">♥</text>
          <rect x="35" y="233" width="260" height="10" fill="#C49A5A" rx="3"/>
          <rect x="20" y="160" width="14" height="78" fill="#D4AA6A"/>
          <rect x="296" y="160" width="14" height="78" fill="#D4AA6A"/>
          <text x="165" y="88" text-anchor="middle" font-size="32" fill="white" opacity="0.7">♥</text>
        </svg>
        <span class="card-badge badge-best">პრემიუმ</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3>✨ "ოცნების სასახლე" — ინდ.</h3>
        <p>სრულად ინდივიდუალური — შენ ირჩევ ფერს, დეკორს, ზომას. ბავშვის ოცნება ჩვენი ამოცანაა!</p>
        <div class="card-specs">
          <span class="spec">📐 2–5 მ²</span>
          <span class="spec">ინდ. ზომა</span>
          <span class="spec">ნებ. ფერი</span>
          <span class="spec">👶 3–14 წ.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <div class="price">₾ შეთ.</div>
          <button class="btn-card" onclick="scrollContact()">კონსულტაცია</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section id="sizes">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-tag">📐 სპეციფიკაციები</span>
    <h2>ზომები და მახასიათებლები</h2>
    <p>სტანდარტული ზომები — ან ინდივიდუალურად მოვარგებთ შენს ეზოს.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="sizes-wrap">
    <table class="sizes-table">
